        .set-5a
          %h4 i) A library of feedback to learn from
          %p All case feedback from others is saved and accessible here for you review at any time
          %p Browse and search through cases you've done
          %p Click on a case in the list on the left to see the record
        .set-5b
          %h4 ii) Case Record
          %p Radar chart showing your scores for each of the sub-criteria. Click on the 'combined' button to see your average scores for the main criteria
          %p Your scores, comments and top 3 recommendations
          %p Smaller radar charts showing your sub-criteria scores. Move your mouse over a point to see the critera name
        .set-5c
          %h4 iii) Radar Chart
          %p xxx
          %p xxx
